==English==
===Noun===
'''velcro'''&reg;<!-- or is the trademark uppercase -->

#A trademarked name for a fastener consisting of two strips of fabric, one covered with minute fiber hooks and the other of tiny fiber loops, when the two are brought together they stick strongly one to the other. Originally made for military clothing, it is very common place now in all sorts of functions.

====Translations====
*[[Interlingua]]: velcro
*Spanish: velcro

===Adjective===
'''velcro'''

#Having this trademarked fastening process.

===Verb===
'''to velcro'''

#to close tight with this trademarked fastening process.